{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8a003903-329b-45d7-b2c5-357775577fb8","content":"There's no project code here, so this is a general guidance answer:\n\n### Changes needed\n\n**1. Remove (or set to `false`) the VSTest flag in your `.csproj`:**\n\n```xml\n<!-- DELETE or change to false -->\n<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n```\n\nWith `MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0`, Microsoft.Testing.Platform is the **default** runner, so simply removing `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` switches you over.\n\n**2. Update your test invocation:**\n\n| Before (VSTest) | After (MS Testing Platform) |\n|---|---|\n| `dotnet test` | `dotnet test` (still works) |\n| `dotnet vstest` | ❌ no longer supported |\n\n`dotnet test` continues to work but now delegates to the new platform under the hood.\n\n**3. Watch for these breaking changes:**\n\n- **`.runsettings`** — most settings still apply, but some VSTest-specific nodes (e.g. `<InProcDataCollectorRunSettings>`) are ignored. Review your `.runsettings` file if you have one.\n- **Command-line args** — VSTest-style CLI options like `--logger \"trx\"` change to `--report-trx`. Run your test project with `--help` to see new options.\n- **Custom adapters/extensions** — any VSTest-specific test adapters won't load; you need their Microsoft.Testing.Platform equivalents.\n\n**4. (Optional) Explicitly opt in** — if you want to be explicit rather than relying on the default:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <UseVSTest>false</UseVSTest>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### TL;DR\n\nRemove `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` — that's the only required change. Then verify your `.runsettings`, CLI arguments, and any custom extensions still work with the new runner.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c0b56394-c62d-4e97-bcfe-a458025f1a67","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The working directory appears to be empty and has no relevant files. This is a general knowledge question about migrating from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform with MSTest.Sdk. Let me answer based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":525,"requestId":"7030:318D8B:DC75832:F2B5B13:69F2A87A"},"id":"78714269-a5dd-4293-bc8d-031e6bb1e46d","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:55:34.803Z","parentId":"d61826fe-ae46-430e-bc02-eb4f56f919e1"}
